channel.title: New Sayyox Design
channel.description:
I'm making a new template since I messed this one up, but this time I know what Im doing...seriously. So this template is basically a show off :|.....
[hr] As you may or may not have noticed, I have put my site under construction since I am making a whole new website for people to come and download web templates. I won't be supporting any runescape content on my website however, I will partner(affiliate) with anyone who is willing to support my site. Anyways, I have been working on the site design for 2 days now and I finally finished it. I went through a lot of websites just to make this one up. I get my inspiration from colors mainly and green(blue too!) is my favorite color Thats why I have green on it. I kinda got creative a with the logo & content box (but if I had my photoshop fixed it would be better because I downloaded scripts from talk-manias site to make cool logos for myself. But I can't use photoshop since no one wont give it to me - well I have it but it just needs repairing and i deleted the repair file by mistake lol.). As you can see I am making wesite templates so if any is interesting in joining my site group that I am developing please do so. Thanks.
Oh yeh, heres the link to see the design lol http://s260.photobucket.com/albums/ii3/Ixl_photos/?action=view&current=Design.png
